						<div class="postbody">I get the same values for the CPU clock rate and resampling ratio for output to 48 kHz.<br /><br />Dumb question, but are you accounting for the APU square running at half the clock rate? That would make the output one octave too high.<br />Alternatively, playing a PAL or Dendy ROM at NTSC rate would also raise the pitch.</div>

